        <script type="text/javascript">
        jQuery(document).ready(function () {
            //setup before functions
            var typingTimer;
            var doneTypingInterval = 1500;
            var $input = jQuery("input#search");
            var page = 2;
            var ajaxurl = "https://tnawrestling.com/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php";
            if ( jQuery("div.search-results").length == 0 ) {
                jQuery("<div class='search-results'></div>").insertBefore('div.footer-container');
            }
            $input.on("keyup change", function(event) {
                clearTimeout(typingTimer);
                typingTimer = setTimeout(function () {
                    var searchVal = jQuery("input#search").val();
                    if ( searchVal.length > 1 ) {
                        jQuery.post(
                            ajaxurl, {
                                'action': 'custom_search_autocomplete',
                                'search' : searchVal
                            }, 
                            function (data) {
                                jQuery('div.search-results').html(data);
                                if ( jQuery('#searchResultPopup .search-custom-width').length >= 8 ) {
                                    jQuery('.see-more').show();
                                }
                                if ( jQuery('#searchResultPopup').length > 0 ) { 
                                    var postCount = jQuery('#searchResultPopup').attr('data-total-post');
                                    load_more_posts(postCount, searchVal);
                                }
                            }
                        );
                    } else {
                        jQuery('div.search-results').html('');
                    }
                }, doneTypingInterval);
            });

            function load_more_posts(Count, searchWord) {
                jQuery("body").on("click","#load-more", function(event) {
                    var ajaxUrl = "https://tnawrestling.com/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php";
                    var total_post = Math.ceil(Count/8);
                    clearTimeout(typingTimer);
                    typingTimer = setTimeout(function () {
                        jQuery(".loader").show();
                        jQuery.post(
                            ajaxurl, {
                                'action': 'more_search_posts',
                                'page' : page,
                                'search' : searchWord
                            },
                            function(posts) {
                                jQuery(".loader").hide();
                                if ( total_post == page) {
                                    jQuery('.see-more').hide();
                                }
                                jQuery('.all-search-posts').append(posts);
                                page++;
                            }
                        );
                    }, doneTypingInterval);
                });
            }
        });
    </script>

var audioPlayer = document.getElementById('audio_player');
var audioPlayerBtn = document.getElementById('soound_button');

function playPause(song){
   if (song.paused && song.currentTime >= 0 && !song.ended) {
      song.play();
   } else {
      song.pause();
   }
}

function reset(btn, song){
   if(btn.classList.contains('playing')){
      btn.classList.toggle('playing');
   }
   song.pause();
   song.currentTime = 0;
}

function progress(btn, song){
   setTimeout(function(){
      var end = song.duration; 
      var current = song.currentTime;
      var percent = current/(end/100);
      //check if song is at the end
      if(current==end){
         reset(btn, song);
      }
      //call function again
      progress(btn, song);     
   }, 1000);
}

audioPlayerBtn.addEventListener('click', function(){
   audioPlayerBtn.classList.toggle('playing');
   playPause(audioPlayer);
   progress(audioPlayerBtn, audioPlayer);
});
